###
### DemeterAI v2.0 - Location Controller HTTP Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### Controller: location_controller.py (C008-C013)
###

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiPrefix = /api/v1/locations

###
### C008: GET - List all warehouses (with pagination)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/warehouses?skip=0&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C008: GET - List all warehouses (default pagination)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/warehouses
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C009: GET - Get warehouse areas (Warehouse ID: 1)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/warehouses/1/areas
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C009: GET - Get warehouse areas (Warehouse ID: 2)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/warehouses/2/areas
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C010: GET - Get storage locations for area (Area ID: 1)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/areas/1/locations
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C010: GET - Get storage locations for area (Area ID: 2)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/areas/2/locations
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C011: GET - Get storage bins for location (Location ID: 1)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/locations/1/bins
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C011: GET - Get storage bins for location (Location ID: 10)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/locations/10/bins
Content-Type: application/json

