GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/search?longitude=-68.7035&latitude=-33.0416
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C012: GET - Search by GPS coordinates (another example)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/search?longitude=-68.7036&latitude=-33.0417
